item.dc:creator: @codyganzell codyganzell
item.description:
@codyganzell wrote:

[quote=“Jordiescape, post:17, topic:236481”]That’d probably have something to do with this;

toX = ####+misc.random(4);

It’ll be something like that. To change the certain teleports you’ll need to search the case ID in clickingmost.java.
Here are the telport case IDs;

case 4140: //Varrock teleport case 4143: // Lumbridge teleport. case 4146: //Falador teleport case 4150: // Camelot teleport case 6004: // Ardounge teleport case 72038: // Ape atoll
There’s some that took me like 1 minute to find out. You can find out the rest.[/quote]
Yes i see. But if I know the case id, where do i change the coords, in clickingmost.java? or in some other java file?
